Juncker Says Ministers Starting Talks on Bank Recapitalization

-- B y   F r e d   P a l s
-- 
2011-10-22T07:06:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/juncker-says-ministers-starting-talks-on-bank-recapitalization.html
European Union finance ministers are
starting talks on bank-recapitalization issues, Luxembourg’s
Jean-Claude Juncker said.  Juncker, who leads the group of euro-area finance
ministers, told reporters in Brussels today that discussions on
how to leverage the firepower of the European Financial
Stability Facility rescue fund are focusing on two options. He
didn’t elaborate.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Pals in Brussels at 
 fpals@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jones Hayden at 
 jhayden1@bloomberg.net  